{
  "stem": "25287.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a museum, and have the Catholic church, the evangelic church, the reform church, and the Greek Catholic, and the Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I needed to wait almost a year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was too young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I want to be always a teacher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And only one Jewish college was in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And because I graduated public school, I needed to make a special test to pass it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they accepted me, but people already came the law that if I go into-- that was after high school, was a four year-- four year or third year, I don't remember, to get the pay, as like here.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then, I couldn't get a job, because I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because our father was hurt and got the medal from the first war, so the high school education till then we was good grade was free for us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I could get state university free, the Jewish university cost money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they said if I finish, I couldn't teach, because I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I was-- think about a very serious girl.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't even know how they thread the needle, but I asked my sister, who was living in Pasadena, maybe I should learn to designing dresses, and dress-making, and then I will teach.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I get the diploma. but you couldn't open up a designing place or teaching-- you needed to have two years really working to get apprenticeship.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then after came the Jewish law-- I couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only just go to the houses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because for working, like a day work, like a cleaning woman-- you could [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And once my younger sister came to help, two horse, a beautiful horse, with-- but I don't know how they call this, the fancy carriage-- and wintertime they even send that to one coat.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
